_sText:
zm_cbble_panic is a map combining the cbble, and lila panic theme.

Since the old version of the map isn't good, i decided to make the 2nd version of the map. This version of the map provides improvement of the 1st version of the map.

It has 64 player spawns, some spots to barricade, or to hold.

Things that have been modified (comparing v1 to v2):

  • The map is now larger than the 1st version, and contains more spots.
  • Insead of daytime, it is now nighttime.
  • All secrets have been removed, and there are no new secrets.
  • Roof are partially accessible. As visible in the screenshots, only the flat surface of the roof are accessible/playable.
  • There are speed boosts in the walkable roof part, just like inÂ lego miniworld.
  • There are now underground/basement level, with two entry ways.

The original map thread:
http://plaguefest.com/threads/zm_cbble_panic_v1fix.20772/

If there are bugs in the map, please notify me and i'll try to fix it.
